            <span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span>
          </span>
          <span class="google-pill-text"><strong>4.9</strong> &middot; 143 reviews on Google</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Painting &amp;<br><span class="h1-brushed"><em class="h1-accent">Decorating</em><svg class="brush-under" viewBox="0 0 240 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M 3,9 C 60,4 120,12 180,7 C 205,5 225,9 237,8 L 237,12 C 225,13 205,9 180,11 C 120,16 60,8 3,13 Z" fill="#E06520" opacity="0.5"/></svg></span><br>Services in Exeter</h1>

        <p class="hero-sub">Expert painters and decorators covering Exeter and East Devon. Fixed-price quotes, premium materials and tidy, reliable work.</p>

        <ul class="hero-bullets">
          <li>
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Fully insured and TrustMark registered
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Free no-obligation quotes within 24 hours
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Dulux Select Decorator, premium materials only
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            17 years serving Exeter and East Devon
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="tel:01392456789" class="btn-primary">
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.62 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 8.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            Call 01392 456789
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        </div>

        </div><!-- end .hero-content -->

        <div class="hero-image">
          <img src="/images/painting/hero.png" alt="Freshly decorated living room with warm feature wall and tidy painting tools" />
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. TRUST BAR -->
    <section class="trust-bar">
      <div class="container trust-inner">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num">17</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Years Trading</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num">600+</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Homes Decorated</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num">4.9<span class="trust-star">★</span></span>
          <span class="trust-label">Google Rating</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num trust-badge">Dulux</span>
          <span class="trust-label">Select Decorator</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. SERVICES -->
    <section id="services" class="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <p class="section-label">What We Offer</p>
          <h2>Our Services</h2>
          <p class="section-sub">From a single feature wall to a full exterior repaint, every job gets the same care and precision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-grid">

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M3 9h18M9 9v12"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Interior Painting</h3>
            <p>Walls, ceilings, woodwork and coving. Thorough preparation and quality emulsions for a finish that lasts.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
                <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Exterior Painting</h3>
            <p>Render, masonry, fascias and guttering. Weather-resistant coatings that protect and transform your property.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
                <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
                <rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
                <rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Wallpaper Hanging</h3>
            <p>Precision hanging for all types, including pattern matching, lining paper and specialist decorative finishes.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/>
                <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Commercial Decorating</h3>
            <p>Offices, retail units and hospitality spaces. Efficient, minimal-disruption work to keep your business running.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
                <line x1="3" y1="14" x2="21" y2="14"/>
                <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Wood Staining &amp; Varnishing</h3>
            <p>Floors, staircases, doors and garden furniture. Protective and decorative finishes applied with care.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
                <rect x="9" y="9" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
                <path d="M9 3v18"/>
                <path d="M3 9h6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Feature Walls</h3>
            <p>Bold colour blocking, specialist textures and decorative finishes that become the centrepiece of any room.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. REVIEWS -->
    <section id="reviews" class="reviews">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <p class="section-label">Customer Reviews</p>
          <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
          <div class="reviews-meta">
            <span class="reviews-stars">★★★★★</span>
            <span class="reviews-score">4.9 out of 5 &middot; 143 Google reviews</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: replace with real reviews -->
        <div class="reviews-grid">
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="review-text">"LJ decorated our whole Victorian terrace from top to bottom. The attention to detail on the cornicing and skirting was immaculate. Couldn't be happier with the result."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="review-avatar">SM</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Sarah Mitchell</strong>
                <span>St Thomas, Exeter</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="review-text">"Reliable, tidy and professional from start to finish. Luke gave us a fixed price and stuck to it. Our sitting room looks completely transformed."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="review-avatar">DH</div>
              <div>
                <strong>David Hartley</strong>
                <span>Topsham, Devon</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="review-text">"Had the kitchen and hallway done in time for Christmas. Finished ahead of schedule, left the house spotless. Genuinely the best tradespeople we've ever used."</p>
            <div class="review-author">
              <div class="review-avatar">CO</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Claire Osman</strong>
                <span>Heavitree, Exeter</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. ABOUT / WHY US -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="container about-inner">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p class="section-label">Why Choose LJ</p>
          <h2>Exeter's Most Trusted Painting &amp; Decorating Specialists</h2>
          <p>Founded in 2008 by Luke James, LJ Painting &amp; Decorating has grown to become one of Exeter's most recommended decorating companies. We work on homes and commercial properties across Devon, always with the same commitment to quality and respect for your space.</p>
          <p>We only use premium paints from Dulux, Farrow &amp; Ball and Little Greene. Every job starts with thorough preparation, because the best finish begins before the paint even opens.</p>
          <ul class="about-list">
            <li>
              <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              TrustMark registered and fully insured
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Fixed-price quotes, never any hidden extras
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Full dust-sheet protection of your home on every job
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Thorough clean-up and tidy-away on completion
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-num">17</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in business</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-num">600+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Satisfied customers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-num">4.9</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Google star rating</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-num">2</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Accreditations held</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. CONTACT FORM -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact">
      <div class="container contact-inner">
        <div class="contact-text">
          <p class="section-label">Get in Touch</p>
          <h2>Get Your Free Quote</h2>
          <p>Tell us about your project and we'll get back to you within 24 hours with a no-obligation price.</p>
          <div class="contact-details">
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.62 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 8.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
              <a href="tel:01392456789">01392 456789</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
              <a href="mailto:hello@ljpainting.co.uk">hello@ljpainting.co.uk</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
              Mon–Fri 8am–6pm, Sat 9am–1pm
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <form class="contact-form" novalidate>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="John Smith" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="01392 ..." />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@email.com" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Tell us about your project</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="e.g. 3-bed house interior, looking to redecorate before Christmas..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary btn-full">Send My Quote Request</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 8. FOOTER -->
    <footer>
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="#" class="logo logo-light">LJ Painting &amp; Decorating</a>
          <p>Painting &amp; Decorating Services<br>Exeter and East Devon</p>
          <div class="footer-socials">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-label="Facebook"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-label="Instagram"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-label="X / Twitter"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <h4>Services</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Interior Painting</li>
            <li>Exterior Painting</li>
            <li>Wallpaper Hanging</li>
            <li>Commercial Decorating</li>
            <li>Wood Staining</li>
            <li>Feature Walls</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-contact">
          <h4>Contact</h4>
          <p>LJ Painting &amp; Decorating<br>Exeter, Devon EX1 1AA</p>
          <p><a href="tel:01392456789">01392 456789</a></p>
          <p><a href="mailto:hello@ljpainting.co.uk">hello@ljpainting.co.uk</a></p>
          <p>Mon–Fri: 8am–6pm<br>Saturday: 9am–1pm</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <div class="container">
          <p>&copy; 2025 LJ Painting &amp; Decorating. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
